name: Josef Charles
text: Great place. Clean . Nice friendly people.

name: Mike Montemaggi
text: Large Thanksgiving Toasted .. Same amount of Turkey on a small!! Bad portions!!! Sub was tasty .. But not worth $8.29!!! Also ..  fix the hand dryer & hot water!! How can you wash your hands properly!?!?! (1/28/18)

name: constance mccue
text: The hamburgers are wonderful and the help very pleasant.

name: Kaysin Enorai
text: Very anti-customer atmosphere. Hours change erratically at this location and have been disrespected myltiple times by employees. Better sub shops are close by.

name: AlwaysBotted
text: I ordered two Large Steak n' cheese sandwiches and on the sizzling savings it says I would get a free sandwich equal or lesser value. I never got my third sandwich, my wife spoke to the Manager and he said it doesn't qualify. Talk about corrupted management!

name: John Rahman
text: Excellent soup and sandwiches. Right near the highway.

name: Liz
text: After waiting to place a phone order for 7 minutes I guess I'll order somewhere else.

name: Bill Densberger
text: Tasty but a bit expensive and a lot more bread that meat and veggies.
